Update from the Programme


Event:  Teacher recruitment and retention and its links to attainment gaps =
in England

Jointly organised in-person seminar at IOE, London, on 30 March 2026, 10:00=
 am - 4:00 pm, organised by BERA in conjunction with the ESRC Education Res=
earch Programme (ERP). The focus will be on two inter-related topics. First=
, the issue of teacher recruitment and retention. Second, how socioeconomic=
 disadvantage and geographical context shape educational outcomes in Englan=
d. Featuring presentations from the ERP's Gemma Moss and Louise Yorke, and =
from Beng Huat See, project member of an ERP project investigating the recr=
uitment and retention of ethnic minority teachers. Booking required.

